    <section id="id1165834365801">
      <title>[LO 4.2.1]</title>
      <para id="id1165834583398">We continue to focus on writing in this activity, but now you are going to <emphasis effect="italics">write a letter</emphasis> to a friend. You are going to imagine that you were staying in the Royal Hotel on holiday when a fire broke out and the hotel burnt down. In your letter you are going to describe the following to your friend:</para>
      <list id="id1165837147544" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
        <item>what you were doing before the fire;</item>
        <item>how you became aware that the fire had broken out;</item>
        <item>how you were rescued from the burning building.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1165834529267">Look at the picture carefully to get some inspiration! </para>
      <para id="id1165832162931">Write your letter. Remember to include your address at the top of the letter and to write in paragraphs.</para>
